rComments: Do not take a class with him unless you want a useless experience. His test was easy but his assignments are boring, long, and brutal. He gave the TA's different marking criteria than he gave the class.

Lectures are useless. Speaks too slowly. Doesn't know what he's talking about. Comes ill prepared to class. Cannot answer student's questions directly because he doesn't know the answers, and when he does answer, it doesn't make sense. Assigns readings and film viewings from the early 1990s. Does not understand Sociological research.
